name: get_5_latest_endpoint
description:
This is a sub-function API for tool currenciesexchangerateapi.
Tool description: CurrenciesRatesAPI is a RESTful API that provides currency conversion and exchange rate information.This API is organized around REST. Our API has predictable resource-oriented URLs, accepts form-encoded request bodies, returns JSON-encoded responses.
API description: Endpoint URL:/latest?symbols=EUR&base=usd
HTTP Method: GET
Request Parameters:
'symbols': 
'base': 
Response: This endpoint returns the latest exchange rates for the specified currencies in JSON format.

symbols.description: Comma-separated list of currency codes to fetch rates for.

base.description: The base currency code against which exchange rates are calculated.
